### Added
- Support builds without Git
- Limit offline username to 16 characters
- [Windows] Support 64-Bit builds
- Allow fractional DPI scaling
- [Windows] Provide portable and system builds
- Improve release workflow

### Changed
- Add license headers
- Improve mod downloads
- Bundle JRE 8u312 for AppImage

### Fixed
- [Linux] Update metainfo URLs
- [Linux] Fix JavaCheck for AppImage
- [macOS] Fix branding
- Clarify license
- [Windows] Fix portable builds
- Improve translations
- Limit instance names' length
- [macOS] Fix loading of WebP images
- Fix buttons on mods page when instance is running
- Statically link remaining internal libraries

### Removed
- Remove paste.polymc.org

